show.description:
A young CEO haunted by the mysterious death of his fiancée begins to question everything—especially when he meets two strangers with her exact face.
One enters his home. One roams the streets. Both hold clues to a buried truth. A thrilling tale of love, deception, and dark secrets where every identity hides a twist.
